00:37:21.927 --> 00:37:26.367 position:30.95%,start align:start size:48.10% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>such a... nice suit.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1295
00:37:29.805 --> 00:37:31.205 position:27.14%,start align:start size:53.81% line:84.62% 
