1298
00:37:33.844 --> 00:37:36.643 position:29.05%,start align:start size:51.90% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>even with surroundings</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1299
00:37:33.844 --> 00:37:36.643 position:29.05%,start align:start size:50.00% line:84.62% 
