<c.white><c.mono_sans>makes it all worthwhile.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1397
00:39:56.921 --> 00:40:00.161 position:36.67%,start align:start size:36.67% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Ah, that alone</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1398
00:40:00.201 --> 00:40:03.199 position:32.86%,start align:start size:44.29% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>You heard the man.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1399
00:40:00.201 --> 00:40:03.199 position:38.57%,start align:start size:30.95% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Get moving.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1400
00:40:03.239 --> 00:40:04.319 position:27.14%,start align:start size:29.05% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Thank you.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1401
00:40:06.558 --> 00:40:07.638 position:38.57%,start align:start size:32.86% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Both of you.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1402
00:40:07.678 --> 00:40:09.798 position:42.38%,start align:start size:36.67% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Yes, yes, yes.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1403
00:40:07.678 --> 00:40:09.798 position:42.38%,start align:start size:48.10% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Go, go, and quickly.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1404
00:40:09.837 --> 00:40:11.477 position:38.57%,start align:start size:51.90% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Keep up the good work.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1405
00:40:28.632 --> 00:40:32.231 position:34.76%,start align:start size:38.57% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Quark, I've got</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1406
00:40:28.632 --> 00:40:32.231 position:34.76%,start align:start size:40.48% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>to say good-bye.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1407
00:40:32.270 --> 00:40:34.702 position:27.14%,start align:start size:50.00% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Oh, just let them go.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1408
00:40:34.110 --> 00:40:35.630 position:19.52%,start align:start size:69.05% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>It'll be less painful that way.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1409
00:40:35.670 --> 00:40:39.509 position:32.86%,start align:start size:57.62% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>No, you don't understand.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1410
00:40:39.549 --> 00:40:42.467 position:23.33%,start align:start size:67.14% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I have to say good-bye to you.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1411
00:40:43.507 --> 00:40:45.278 position:42.38%,start align:start size:48.10% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I'm going with them.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1412
00:40:45.671 --> 00:40:46.826 position:19.52%,start align:start size:44.29% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>But we had a deal.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1413
00:40:46.866 --> 00:40:48.626 position:46.19%,start align:start size:44.29% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I can't stay here.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1414
00:40:48.666 --> 00:40:52.584 position:23.33%,start align:start size:65.24% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Maybe one day I can come back</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1415
00:40:48.666 --> 00:40:52.584 position:23.33%,start align:start size:61.43% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>and we'll be together again</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1416
00:40:52.625 --> 00:40:54.904 position:23.33%,start align:start size:67.14% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>but not until my work is done.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1417
00:40:54.944 --> 00:40:57.630 position:30.95%,start align:start size:48.10% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>So, all I have to do</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1418
00:40:54.944 --> 00:40:57.630 position:34.76%,start align:start size:38.57% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>to get you back</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1419
00:40:57.103 --> 00:41:00.227 position:19.52%,start align:start size:69.05% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>is wait until Cardassia becomes</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1420
00:40:57.103 --> 00:41:00.227 position:19.52%,start align:start size:67.14% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>a free and democratic society?</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1421
00:41:03.661 --> 00:41:06.610 position:57.62%,start align:start size:32.86% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I promise...</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1422
00:41:06.101 --> 00:41:08.180 position:51.90%,start align:start size:32.86% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I'll make it</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1423
00:41:06.101 --> 00:41:08.180 position:51.90%,start align:start size:38.57% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>worth the wait.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1424
00:41:20.136 --> 00:41:23.935 position:29.05%,start align:start size:51.90% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I could come with you.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1425
00:41:20.136 --> 00:41:23.935 position:34.76%,start align:start size:38.57% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I don't suppose</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1426
00:41:23.975 --> 00:41:27.613 position:27.14%,start align:start size:55.71% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>No, it's not your fight.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1427
00:41:27.654 --> 00:41:29.733 position:29.05%,start align:start size:51.90% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Besides, I could never</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1428
00:41:27.654 --> 00:41:29.733 position:34.76%,start align:start size:40.48% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>live with myself</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1429
00:41:29.773 --> 00:41:31.653 position:25.24%,start align:start size:65.24% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>if something happened to you.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1430
00:41:31.693 --> 00:41:34.932 position:44.29%,start align:start size:46.19% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I need to know that</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1431
00:41:31.693 --> 00:41:34.932 position:44.29%,start align:start size:44.29% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>you're here, safe.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1432
00:41:34.972 --> 00:41:38.330 position:30.95%,start align:start size:51.90% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>That way, a part of</c.mono_sans></c.white><c.white><c.mono_sans><i> me</i></c.mono_sans></c.white>

1433
00:41:34.972 --> 00:41:38.330 position:30.95%,start align:start size:57.62% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>will always be safe, too.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1434
00:41:47.328 --> 00:41:48.927 position:46.19%,start align:start size:44.29% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I love you, Quark.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1435
00:41:50.607 --> 00:41:52.127 position:42.38%,start align:start size:36.67% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I always will.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1436
00:42:07.442 --> 00:42:08.921 position:34.76%,start align:start size:40.48% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I love you, too.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1437
00:42:12.441 --> 00:42:15.919 position:19.52%,start align:start size:46.19% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I suggest we return</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1438
00:42:12.441 --> 00:42:15.919 position:19.52%,start align:start size:69.05% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>to the Promenade without delay.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1439
00:42:17.320 --> 00:42:20.786 position:42.38%,start align:start size:48.10% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>You have to tell me.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1440
00:42:17.320 --> 00:42:20.786 position:42.38%,start align:start size:44.29% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Why did you do it?</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1441
00:42:20.118 --> 00:42:21.238 position:57.62%,start align:start size:32.86% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Shoot Toran.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1442
00:42:21.279 --> 00:42:23.637 position:19.52%,start align:start size:50.00% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Well, why did you let</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1443
00:42:21.279 --> 00:42:23.637 position:19.52%,start align:start size:44.29% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Professor Lang go?</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1444
00:42:23.677 --> 00:42:26.116 position:48.10%,start align:start size:42.38% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I have no choice.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1445
00:42:23.677 --> 00:42:26.116 position:48.10%,start align:start size:30.95% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I love her.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1446
00:42:26.156 --> 00:42:28.756 position:19.52%,start align:start size:50.00% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>And I love Cardassia,</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1447
00:42:28.115 --> 00:42:30.276 position:19.52%,start align:start size:32.86% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>which is why</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1448
00:42:28.115 --> 00:42:30.276 position:19.52%,start align:start size:53.81% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I had to do what I did.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1449
00:42:32.475 --> 00:42:34.994 position:44.29%,start align:start size:46.19% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I don't understand.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1450
00:42:35.342 --> 00:42:37.735 position:19.52%,start align:start size:63.33% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>That's the thing about love.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1451
00:42:37.113 --> 00:42:39.672 position:19.52%,start align:start size:34.76% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>No one really</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1452
00:42:37.113 --> 00:42:39.672 position:19.52%,start align:start size:55.71% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>understands it, do they?</c.mono_sans></c.white>

